  "text": "## Common Complaint Scenarios & Resolutions  \n### Scenario 1: Failed Transfer (Not Refunded)  \n**Your Issue:** \"I tried to transfer £500 but it failed. Money was taken from my account.\"  \n**What We Investigate:**\n- Did the transfer actually complete or fail?\n- If failed, was the money debited or not?\n- Why did it fail?  \n**Possible Outcomes:**\n- **Authorized:** No fee charged (system error); refund + interest\n- **Insufficient funds:** Explain why it failed; no refund\n- **Invalid recipient:** Explain error; refund if our fault  \n**Typical Resolution Time:** 2–3 business days  \n---",
